lesbar
------------------------------------------
lesbar is a programming language agnostic view layer for creating desktop
widgets and status bars.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.4.3-1
  libX11_6-1.8.1-1
  libcairo2-1.17.4-1
  libglib2.0_0-2.54.3-1
  libpango1.0_0-1.40.14-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.39-1
  cygport-0.35.5-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  libX11-devel-1.8.1-1
  libcairo-devel-1.17.4-1
  libglib2.0-devel-2.54.3-1
  libpango1.0-devel-1.40.14-1
  make-4.4-1
  scdoc-1.11.2-1bl2

Canonical website:
  https://git.sr.ht/~salmiak/lesbar

Canonical download:
  https://git.sr.ht/~salmiak/lesbar

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack lesbar-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./lesbar-1.0.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/lesbar-1.0.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/lesbar-1.0.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(lesbar)
  /usr/bin/lesbar.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/lesbar.README
  /usr/share/doc/lesbar/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/lesbar/README.md
  /usr/share/man/man1/lesbar.1.gz

